HOUSE BILL 876
By White
SENATE BILL 797
By Haile
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 8,
Chapter 50, relative to continuing education for
state employees.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 8-50-114(h), is amended by
designating the existing language as subdivision (1) and adding the following subdivision (2):
(2) Subdivision (h)(1) applies to full-time employees of the general assembly
who work more hours each week than typically required of full-time employment for at
least four (4) weeks per year.
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
